"title": "8437: giving, of talents",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8437",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All human abilities and skills derive from God and are to be dedicated to his glory and the good of others.</p>\n<h2>Talents are given and sustained by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:7\">1CO 4:7</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:3\">EXO 28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:3-Exod31:6\">EXO 31:3–31:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:31-Exod35:35\">EXO 35:31–35:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:1-Exod36:2\">EXO 36:1–36:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:34-2Sam22:35\">2SA 22:34–22:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:33-Ps18:34\">PSA 18:33–18:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:15\">MAT 25:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:13\">LUK 19:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:10\">ACT 7:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6\">ROM 12:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7-1Cor12:8\">1CO 12:7–12:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:5\">2CO 3:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:7\">EPH 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:7\">EPH 4:7</a></p>\n<h2>Talents differ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:15\">MAT 25:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:6\">ROM 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:7\">1CO 7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:6\">1CO 12:4–12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11\">EPH 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>Talents need to be developed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:6\">2TI 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:16-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:16–25:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:12-Luke19:26\">LUK 19:12–19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:14\">1TI 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Talents are to be devoted to God</h2>\n<h3>For his own glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:11\">1PE 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:10\">EXO 35:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:25\">EXO 35:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:40\">1KI 7:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr9:13\">1CH 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:2-Ps33:3\">PSA 33:2–33:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:4-Ps137:5\">PSA 137:4–137:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:31\">1CO 10:31</a></p>\n<h3>For the good of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:10\">1PE 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7\">1CO 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:12\">1CO 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12\">EPH 4:12</a></p>\n<h2>Talents are to be accounted for</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:19\">MAT 25:19</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:15\">LUK 19:15</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:34\">MAT 21:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:2\">MRK 12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:10\">LUK 20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:48\">LUK 12:48</a></p>\n<h2>Rewards according to use or misuse of talents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">MAT 25:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:23-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:23–25:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:17-Luke19:26\">LUK 19:17–19:26</a></p>",
